---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use — Chartedly" isArticle={true}>
  <div class="max-w-[768px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 py-8">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">利用規約</p>

    <p class="text-sm mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Agreement</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        By accessing and using Chartedly (chartedly.com), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">About the Service</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        Chartedly is a product comparison and review website focused on products available in Japan. We provide scores, rankings, and editorial recommendations to help consumers make informed purchasing decisions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Content and Accuracy</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        We make every effort to provide accurate, up-to-date product information. However, prices, availability, and product specifications change frequently. Chartedly does not guarantee the accuracy or completeness of any information on the site.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        Product scores represent our editorial assessment and are intended as guidance, not absolute measures of quality. Individual experiences may vary.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        Chartedly contains affiliate links. When you purchase products through these links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial rankings or recommendations. See our <a href="/about#affiliate-disclosure" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); text-decoration: underline;">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        All content on Chartedly, including text, graphics, scores, and the scoring methodology, is the intellectual property of LAIRIA and is protected by applicable copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or republish content from this site without prior written permission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        Chartedly is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of the site or reliance on the information provided. Product purchases are transactions between you and the retailer; Chartedly is not a party to those transactions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        These terms are governed by the laws of Japan. Any disputes arising from the use of this site shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Tokyo District Court.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms. Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@chartedly.com" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); text-decoration: underline;">hello@chartedly.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
